      "text": [
        "اللَّهُمَّ احْمِلْنِي عَلَى عَفْوِكَ، وَلاَ تَحْمِلْنِي عَلَى عدْلِكَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "O My Allāh! Deal with me through Thy forgiveness and do not deal with me according to Thy justice."
        ]
      }
    }
